* Iron Raptor saw Prowl transform back into robot mode, sighing in relief 
that the threat was over. She walked towards him a little and then stopped, 
wanting to rest a little because her shaken systems were trying to recover. 
She wished that she could recover as quickly as Prowl, but she had been the 
source of that sound so it hurt her more then it did him. But it did the 
trick.*

" Prowl?"

* She wanted to know if he was alright, and her head hurt far too much to 
think and communicate with him that way.*
